About this item

  • HANES SCRUBS - Made for those who make a difference. Medical scrubs are appropriate for use in healthcare settings such as hospitals, doctor’s offices, and long-term care facilities.
  • STORAGE DETAILS - Scrub joggers for women have two deep hand pockets and two large cargo pockets for plenty of room to stow the essentials.
  • JOGGER STYLING - Scrub cargo joggers feature an adjustable drawstring, elastic waistband, and comfortable cuffed ankles.
  • MADE TO LAST - Sturdy stretch fabric is designed for lasting wash and wear needs.
  • STAY COOL & FEEL FRESH - Cool Comfort fabric wicks moisture from the skin, while odor control keeps you feeling fresh.
  • FIND YOUR SIZE - Available in a wide range of sizes, including plus size scrub joggers up to 3XL.

Description

Scrubs that work as hard as you do. Introducing Hanes Comfort Fit Scrubs - a perfect blend of comfort, innovation, style, and value. Our scrubs stretch in all the right places to flatter your frame and come in an array of sizes for all body types. And with a comfortable stretch to keep you going all day, our Hanes Comfort Fit Scrub Joggers also come with four pockets- including a roomy utility pocket - so you can work your shift in ease. Hanes Comfort Fit Scrubs - make yourself comfortable.

    If you are on the heavy side like I am, we know that scrubs are the best pants to wear because it dries fast and helps avoid friction between legs... However... This is the first time I have bought a 3XL that feels way too big. Anyway, it's not all bad. There's more pros, but one issue was a deal breaker for me.     Pros:
    1. The measurement is accurate,
    2. Feels nice on the stomach
    3. Plenty nice room around the legs
    2. Good inseam, plenty of room for adjustment-- so tall or short person can wear (just cut the excess fabric)

    Cons:
    1. The rise is way too deep. Like deeeeeep, it almost reached the top of my leg! Which then defies the purpose of buying it in the first place (avoiding friction between legs).
